181
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:11,020
Meat and chicken are extremely expensive,

182
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:13,780
if you can even find them.”

183
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:15,490
One’s that’s basically turned into

184
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:18,780
